{"tid":1595558,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角警署有人不安全高空工作","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T10:40:23.000Z","uid":163502,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cf506b9ddd092b012fda97af35f0e7eefe92c61a","tid":1595558,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYy1GF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYy1GF4.jpg&h=82f93058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勞工處提醒，工人必須配合及遵守僱主制訂的安全規定，亦同時呼籲僱員平日工作時要多加留意周遭情況，如發現不安全的作業模式或環境狀況，應立刻向勞工處作出舉報。勞工處解釋，僱員最清楚每天工作地點的潛在危險，所提供的資料對改善工作安全環境至為重要，除了可以保障自己和其他工友的工作安全外，亦可使家人更安心。<br />\n<br />\n勞工處<br />\n職安健投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/ld0001/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fld0001%2Ftc%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRnO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=be61a69a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/ld0001/tc/</a>"},{"pid":"5883990b6919975dddffeaf08fd4fc870baa5115","tid":1595558,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/307687/%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E8%99%95%E6%8E%A8%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%81%B7%E5%AE%89%E5%81%A5%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-%E5%83%B1%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%82%B3%E7%89%87%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F307687%2F%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%2583%25B1%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%2588%2589%25E5